channel.title: [508] bulby/tokkul-scape based, what frame to remove in playerbank.java for bank
channel.description: the bank name is "i like to leech" and i found out i need to remove a frame from in playerbank.java, could i get some help here?

item.title: [508] bulby/tokkul-scape based, what frame to remove in playerbank.java for bank
item.dc:creator: @gizmos gizmos
item.description:
@gizmos wrote:

thats easy go in player.java look for frames.setBankOptions(this);
under that add frames.setString(this, “banknamehere” , 762, 24);
